1451
01:06:10,600 --> 01:06:11,600
What are gluons like?

1452
01:06:11,600 --> 01:06:14,600
What quantities do gluons have?

1453
01:06:14,600 --> 01:06:16,600
Photons are pretty,

1454
01:06:16,600 --> 01:06:18,600
in a certain sense, uninteresting,

1455
01:06:18,600 --> 01:06:20,600
