1456
01:06:20,600 --> 01:06:21,600
They have a spin.

1457
01:06:21,600 --> 01:06:23,600
They have a polarization.

1458
01:06:23,600 --> 01:06:24,600
They have a momentum,

1459
01:06:24,600 --> 01:06:26,600
and they have a polarization.

1460
01:06:26,600 --> 01:06:27,600
And that's about all.

1461
01:06:27,600 --> 01:06:30,600
They don't have any charge.

1462
01:06:30,600 --> 01:06:35,600
By itself, a photon,

1463
