if it collides with another photon,

1464
01:06:38,600 --> 01:06:40,600
there are no forces.

1465
01:06:40,600 --> 01:06:43,600
Now, that's not exactly true.

1466
01:06:43,600 --> 01:06:45,600
There are forces between photons,

1467
