1470
01:06:51,600 --> 01:06:53,600
They're secondary effects,

1471
01:06:53,600 --> 01:06:55,600
which come from quantum electrodynamics

1472
01:06:55,600 --> 01:06:58,600
and loops of quantum complicated

1473
01:06:58,600 --> 01:07:00,600
Feynman diagrams involving electrons.

1474
01:07:00,600 --> 01:07:03,600
But the primordial interaction between photons

1475
01:07:03,600 --> 01:07:05,600
